---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-marine to-marine-light text-white py-20 pb-15">
  <!-- Decorative circle -->
  <div class="absolute -right-24 -top-24 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(217,123,61,0.15)_0%,transparent_70%)] rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-5 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] gap-15 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Text -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-sans text-[32px] lg:text-[42px] font-extrabold leading-[1.15] mb-5">
          Vous entendez moins bien ?<br />
          <span class="text-orange">On vous explique tout.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[19px] leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-8">
          Perte auditive, appareils, remboursement, acouphenes... Des guides clairs, ecrits par un audioprothesiste independant. Pas de jargon, pas de publicite deguisee — juste l'essentiel pour prendre les bonnes decisions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="/guides/remboursement/"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-orange text-white font-sans text-base font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-hover transition-colors no-underline hover:no-underline"
          >
            Comprendre le remboursement &rarr;
          </a>
          <a
            href="/comparatifs/meilleur-appareil-auditif-2026/"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-transparent text-white font-sans text-base font-semibold rounded-lg border-2 border-white/40 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors no-underline hover:no-underline"
          >
            Voir le comparatif 2026
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Author Card -->
      <div class="bg-white/8 border border-white/15 rounded-2xl p-7 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-orange rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-4 border-3 border-white/30 font-sans font-bold">
          FO
        </div>
        <div class="font-sans text-xl font-bold mb-1">Franck-Olivier</div>
        <div class="font-sans text-[15px] opacity-80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Audioprothesiste diplome d'Etat<br />25+ ans d'experience — 18 centres Alain Afflelou
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/12 border border-white/20 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full font-sans text-[13px] font-medium">
            &#x1F393; Diplome d'Etat
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/12 border border-white/20 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full font-sans text-[13px] font-medium">
            &#x1F3E5; 25 ans terrain
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/12 border border-white/20 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full font-sans text-[13px] font-medium">
            &#x1F52C; 100% independant
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
